snippet: Hull City have signed England defender Michael Dawson on a three-year contract from Tottenham Hotspur, the Premier League club said on their website (www.hullcitytigers.com) on Tuesday....

headline.print_headline: Hull Sign Defender Dawson From Spurs
headline.main: Hull Sign Defender Dawson From Spurs

lead_paragraph: Hull City have signed England defender Michael Dawson on a three-year contract from Tottenham Hotspur, the Premier League club said on their website (www.hullcitytigers.com) on Tuesday.
